{"tid":129395,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Auntie，I will show you the way of life","createTime":"2017-02-21T14:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T03:00:55.000Z","uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d92786fb4f8967cef56c9694bf233b6826ecdeca","tid":129395,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:13:49.000Z","msg":"戴胸圍聲請漢 涉非禮妻子六旬姨媽<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】提出酷刑聲請而留港的西非岡比亞男子，被指闖入妻子的六旬姨媽家中，戴上姨媽的肉色胸圍後向她揚言「Auntie，I will show you the way of life （姨媽，我將向你展示生活之道）」，隨即涉嫌把她推倒床上並撫摸非禮，並一度想張開她雙腿。姨媽遂指自己已是「老女人」，又反抗咬他兼斥責「神會懲罰你」，終成功阻止他進一步侵犯。男子事後被捕，被控傷人及非禮共兩罪，案件於區院開審。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱要展示生活之道<br />\n<br />\n卅四歲男被告被控在前年十二月十三日，在屯門一單位中非禮及傷害港人女事主X（六十四歲）。身為傳教士的Ｘ昨日供稱，事發的樓宇是她父母物業，被告住在她隔鄰單位，被告妻子當時則身在美國。事發傍晚六時，她回家見大門沒上鎖，以為家傭忘記關門，沒有多想便入內。她坐在梳化期間，突然聽到背後有聲，赫然發現被告正身穿沒有拉上拉鏈的連帽衞衣，戴着她的胸圍，並揚言要向她展示生活之道。<br />\n<br />\n被告繼而推她落床壓着她下半身並摸她上身，又試圖想張開她雙腿，她遂咬被告的手以反抗，並喝罵被告為何這樣，又指自己已是「old lady （老女人）」等。被告則圖用枕頭及被單等封她口，但不成功。<br />\n<br />\nX最後撞開被告，被告這時跪下要求她不要張揚此事，X最終通知表妹報警。Ｘ接受辯方盤問時，否認因對被告存有偏見或想趕走被告，而作出誣陷。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC 261/2016<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170221/00176_121.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170221%2F00176_121.html&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0Jlb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=c577915d\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170221/00176_121.html</a>"},{"pid":"fba79ec956f89ff233d39c5d6907506370e09d3e","tid":129395,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cf9d049fa072c9b2356e2c92aa41c54e8baaa6","tid":129395,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"eba1c3a76e2ebf156595b355f7b70ffef9a3f5cc","tid":129395,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafd130589f78b0b05cb0da003a066d13727f36e","tid":129395,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:22:14.000Z","msg":"old lady唔識貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一話 如果係死港女聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f4a55df7a365c549f5e77ed2532eada6aa84a5","tid":129395,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T23:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a83ff439d0e293caabdfffc3c4b2b3353487842","tid":129395,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T03:00:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}